casebody.data:
General Electric Employees Federal Credit Union v. Peter S. Zakrzewski (13651)

O’Connell, Poti and Landau, Js.

Submitted on briefs November 3 decision released November 29, 1994 David E. Koskoff filed a brief for the appellant (defendant). Per Curiam.

The case is controlled by Staples v. Hendrick, 89 Conn. 100, 93 A. 5 (1915).

The judgment is affirmed.
